<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Virtual Assistant Portfolio</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #fff7f9;
      color: #333;
    }

    header {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #f8cdda, #fcb69f);
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    section {
      padding: 40px 20px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #e08ca0;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .contact {
      text-align: center;
      background: #ffe3ec;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 15px;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Azeezat | Virtual Assistant</h1>
    <p>Helping businesses stay organized, efficient & stress-free</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p>
        Hi! I’m a detail-oriented Virtual Assistant skilled in administrative support,
        social media management, and customer service. I help businesses stay organized
        and grow efficiently while saving time and reducing stress.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Services I Offer</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <ul>
        <li>Email Management</li>
        <li>Calendar Scheduling</li>
        <li>Data Entry</li>
        <li>Social Media Management</li>
        <li>Customer Support</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Tools I Use</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <ul>
        <li>Google Workspace</li>
        <li>Microsoft Office</li>
        <li>Canva</li>
        <li>Trello</li>
        <li>Slack</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Sample Projects</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Email Management System</h3>
      <p>Organized inbox for a client and reduced unread emails by 80%.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Social Media Content Plan</h3>
      <p>Created a 30-day content calendar and designed engaging posts.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Data Entry Project</h3>
      <p>Entered and cleaned 500+ records using Excel with high accuracy.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Contact Me</h2>
    <div class="contact">
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> your@email.com</p>
      <p><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> +234XXXXXXXXXX</p>
      <p><strong>LinkedIn:</strong> your-linkedin-profile</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2026 Azeezat | Virtual Assistant</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
